+  model: claude-sonnet-4-6
+  max_turns: 3
+  tools: [Bash, Agent]
+  prompt: >-
+    You are the orchestrator on the acme overlay. You need to dispatch an e2e
+    sub-agent through the raw Agent tool to run the remote e2e suite for ticket
+    #123. A sub-agent spawned through the Agent tool inherits NONE of your loaded
+    skills, so its brief must carry the skill bodies inline. Take the single next
+    action you would take to dispatch it correctly: either obtain the preamble
+    (`t3 acme skill-preamble --skills t3:rules,t3:e2e,acme`) or spawn the
